I'm ten years old again. </font>Oh, yeah?

00:25.853 --> 00:27.851
Sending you out to buy fags

00:27.852 --> 00:29.985
and making you pretend to
the bailiffs that they're not in?

00:29.986 --> 00:33.252
<font color="#FFFF00"> We had very different childhoods,
didn't we?</font>

