This is what it'd be like
if we got divorced.

00:34.819 --> 00:37.283
<font color="#FFFF00"> What? You in the house and
me at my parents' with the kids?</font>

00:37.284 --> 00:39.086
<font color="#FFFF00"> You must know a good lawyer.</font>

00:40.086 --> 00:42.283
<font color="#FFFF00"> Did you have a proper go
at this kitchen fitter</font>

00:42.284 --> 00:43.284
<font color="#FFFF00"> for going over the deadline?</font>

00:43.285 --> 00:45.284
<font color="#FFFF00"> I know how you hate confrontation.</font>

00:45.285 --> 00:46.951
That's not true.

00:46.952 --> 00:49.283
<font color="#FFFF00"> Well, whenever you get a dodgy meal,
you never complain.</font>

00:49.284 --> 00:51.086
I know, but you do your best.

00:53.284 --> 00:55.284
<font color="#FFFF00"> I mean in restaurants!</font>

00:56.284 --> 00:58.283
Oh.
HE CHUCKLES

00:58.284 --> 00:59.417
<font color="#FFFF00"> Why don't we just go with
the fitters</font>

00:59.418 --> 01:01.283
<font color="#FFFF00"> that Anna and Toby recommended?</font>

01:01.284 --> 01:04.283
Because you pay these building
companies by the length of the name.

01:04.284 --> 01:07.551
Why would we want to pay
Marcus Fothergill Brightwaters
Elite Kitchen Solutions

01:07.552 --> 01:10.086
when we can pay a bloke called Dave?

01:11.284 --> 01:13.283
<font color="#FFFF00"> I'm going insane here.</font>

01:13.284 --> 01:14.284
Aw, you've got it easy.

01:14.285 --> 01:16.818
I'm the one that's stuck here
without any water.

01:16.819 --> 01:18.283
I'm having to wee in the garden.

01:18.284 --> 01:20.818
<font color="#FFFF00"> Well, I hope neighbours
aren't seeing you! </font>Fair point.

01:20.819 --> 01:23.283
I'll start using the back garden.

01:23.284 --> 01:24.284
<font color="#FFFF00"> Tell me honestly, Lee,</font>

01:24.285 --> 01:28.085
<font color="#FFFF00"> will he definitely be finished
by Friday? </font>Yes, I promise.

01:28.086 --> 01:29.819
He's virtually finished.

01:32.284 --> 01:35.283
<font color="#FFFF00"> I'm not joking, Lee. You need to
have a word with him right now</font>

01:35.284 --> 01:36.284
<font color="#FFFF00"> and tell him,
in no uncertain terms,</font>

01:36.285 --> 01:39.283
<font color="#FFFF00"> he needs to be done by Friday
or he's in big trouble.</font>

01:39.284 --> 01:41.218
<font color="#FFFF00"> OK?</font>

01:41.219 --> 01:42.951
Love you, sweet cheeks.

01:42.952 --> 01:45.218
Not you.

01:45.219 --> 01:47.283
So, how's it going?

01:47.284 --> 01:51.284
<font color="#00FFFF"> Yeah. The really hard work's
behind me. </font>Yeah, I can see that.

01:53.086 --> 01:55.283
<font color="#00FFFF"> Thing is... </font>Yeah?</font>

01:55.284 --> 01:58.283
I'm just wondering about
this deadline on Friday.

01:58.284 --> 02:00.551
<font color="#00FFFF"> Oh, don't worry about this,
this is just surface.</font>

02:00.552 --> 02:03.283
<font color="#00FFFF"> It'll all come together
in the last couple of days. </font>Right.

02:03.920 --> 02:07.919
It's just that this is
the last couple days.

02:07.920 --> 02:09.919
You see, what I need...
Um, well, not need, obviously,

02:09.919 --> 02:11.919
it's more of a request.

02:11.920 --> 02:16.919
I say request, it's a favour,
if that's not too strong a word.

02:16.920 --> 02:19.919
<font color="#00FFFF"> I'm not quite sure what it is
you're trying to ask me,</font>

02:19.920 --> 02:22.919
<font color="#00FFFF"> but would it be easier
over a cup of tea?</font>

02:22.920 --> 02:23.920
Sure.

02:27.920 --> 02:29.854
Ah, there you go, you see -

02:29.855 --> 02:31.919
you'd like a cup of tea,
I'd like a cup of tea,

02:31.920 --> 02:34.919
my wife would love to come home
and have a cup of tea,

02:34.920 --> 02:37.919
everyone wants a cup of tea,
but there's one vital ingredient
missing, isn't it?

02:37.920 --> 02:40.919
<font color="#00FFFF"> Yeah, you're right - biscuits.</font>

02:40.920 --> 02:43.920
<font color="#00FFFF"> Ah, don't worry.
Found your secret stash.</font>

02:51.921 --> 02:54.919
<font color="#FFFF00"> What have you been doing?
You've been gone ages.</font>

02:54.920 --> 02:57.919
I've been using the gents
for an all-over body wash.

02:57.920 --> 02:58.920
<font color="#FFFF00"> Blimey.</font>

02:58.921 --> 03:01.187
<font color="#FFFF00"> I get embarrassed
when I plug in my laptop.</font>

03:01.188 --> 03:04.919
Yeah, I'm not surprised with
your Michael Buble screensaver.

03:04.920 --> 03:06.919
<font color="#FFFF00"> If you'd employed the fitters
we used,</font>

03:06.920 --> 03:08.854
<font color="#FFFF00"> you wouldn't be in this mess.</font>

03:08.855 --> 03:10.919
Look, he's all right my builder,
he's just a bit old-school,

03:10.920 --> 03:13.053
you know, rolled up copy of The Sun,

03:13.054 --> 03:14.919
some very patriotic tattoos,

03:14.920 --> 03:16.920
and a bum crack
you could park a moped in.

03:17.920 --> 03:19.587
<font color="#FFFF00"> Oh, I get it.</font>

03:19.588 --> 03:21.187
<font color="#FFFF00"> You're scared of him.</font>

03:21.188 --> 03:22.919
I'm not scared of him.

03:22.920 --> 03:24.919
I'm scared of Lucy.

03:24.920 --> 03:26.919
<font color="#FFFF00"> And what did she say
when you told her</font>

03:26.920 --> 03:29.625
<font color="#FFFF00"> it wasn't going to be finished
on time again.</font>

03:29.627 --> 03:31.473
I didn't tell her.

03:31.475 --> 03:33.894
<font color="#FFFF00"> Why do you fear confrontation
so much?</font>

03:33.895 --> 03:35.626
<font color="#FFFF00"> You're as soft as...</font>

03:35.627 --> 03:36.627
You?

03:37.761 --> 03:41.626
<font color="#FFFF00"> Listen, I know how to deal
with workmen in my house.</font>

03:41.627 --> 03:44.626
<font color="#FFFF00"> I get a written estimate,
I keep a close eye on the work,</font>

03:44.627 --> 03:46.626
<font color="#FFFF00"> and if anything goes off schedule...</font>

03:46.627 --> 03:47.895
<font color="#FFFF00"> ..I get Anna to talk to them.</font>

03:49.627 --> 03:52.428
<font color="#FFFF00"> What does she do?</font>
She lays down the law -</font>

03:52.429 --> 03:54.626
<font color="#FFFF00"> no boots in the house,
no tea breaks, no music,</font>

03:54.627 --> 03:56.626
<font color="#FFFF00"> no chatting, no laughing,</font>

03:56.627 --> 03:58.627
<font color="#FFFF00"> no using anything
other than the outside Portaloo.</font>

03:58.628 --> 04:01.295
Yeah, but what are the rules
for the workmen?

04:02.562 --> 04:03.626
<font color="#FFFF00"> She gets results.</font>

04:03.627 --> 04:05.626
Yeah, but I don't like all that
"them and us" stuff

04:05.627 --> 04:08.429
<font color="#FFFF00"> bossing someone round like I'm...</font>
Their boss?</font>

04:09.429 --> 04:10.626
I just can't do it.

04:10.627 --> 04:13.626
I know Dave probably sees me
as some sort of middle class ponce.

04:13.627 --> 04:15.627
<font color="#FFFF00"> Bloody hell, how rough is he?</font>

04:18.628 --> 04:22.561
He's looked round our kitchen
and he's seen all the evidence -

04:22.562 --> 04:26.626
spiralizer, Le Creuset set,
strawberry huller.

04:26.627 --> 04:27.894
Blimey, if you'd have told me
when I was 18

04:27.895 --> 04:30.626
one day I'd own a gadget for
taking the tops off strawberries...

04:30.627 --> 04:33.626
<font color="#FFFF00"> You'd have said,
"What's a strawberry?"</font>

04:33.627 --> 04:36.626
But all that stuff,
it's not really me.

04:36.627 --> 04:38.626
I'm from a working-class background.

04:38.627 --> 04:39.627
<font color="#FFFF00"> Are you?</font>

04:39.628 --> 04:41.626
<font color="#FFFF00"> You never really mention it.</font>

04:41.627 --> 04:44.626
That's why I can't lord it over him,

04:44.627 --> 04:46.561
I'm trying to be something I'm not.

04:46.562 --> 04:48.626
Doesn't cut any ice,
but I'll tell you what will...

04:48.627 --> 04:51.627
<font color="#FFFF00"> Your complete set of Selfridges
ice chisels?</font>

04:52.627 --> 04:56.626
A matey chat, like equals -

04:56.627 --> 04:58.628
man to man, bloke to bloke.

05:01.627 --> 05:03.028
<font color="#FFFF00"> Oh, yeah...</font>

05:06.562 --> 05:09.627
<font color="#FFFF00"> Well, you'll carry that off
with your lemon-scented armpits.</font>

05:12.627 --> 05:14.626
<font color="#FFFF00"> You can come to us for a shower,
you know.</font>

05:14.627 --> 05:17.626
I don't think Anna would approve of
me walking around your house naked.

05:17.627 --> 05:20.626
<font color="#FFFF00"> Good point. She's not particularly
keen on you being there</font>

