06:17.761 --> 06:19.626
<font color="#00FFFF"> Oh, yeah? Builder were you?</font>
Oh, yeah.

06:19.627 --> 06:22.627
Worked with my hands for years -
on the sites, down the docks,

06:22.628 --> 06:24.626
in the... woods.

06:24.627 --> 06:27.626
I've done it all, me -
pointing, grouting...

06:27.627 --> 06:29.626
..flossing.

06:29.627 --> 06:32.626
Some of the stuff I used to
get up to. Oh, I used to...

06:32.627 --> 06:34.626
I did all the tricks, me,
you know. Oh!

06:34.627 --> 06:37.428
Glues not screws,
if all else fails, bang in nails,

06:37.429 --> 06:39.626
extended coffee breaks,
crafty fags...

06:39.627 --> 06:41.627
<font color="#00FFFF"> Peeing in the sink. </font>What?

