<font color="#00FFFF"> Only joking.</font>

06:44.628 --> 06:47.626
Yeah, I know that,
you're not like other builders.

06:47.627 --> 06:50.626
In fact, in a lot of ways,
you're not like a builder at all.

06:50.627 --> 06:52.428
<font color="#00FFFF"> Cheers, mate, it's nice to hear</font>

06:52.429 --> 06:55.626
<font color="#00FFFF"> cos I did wonder if you're a bit
narked about the pace of the job.</font>

06:55.627 --> 06:57.626
Narked? Don't be silly, mate.

06:57.627 --> 07:00.027
Eh? It takes as long as it takes.

07:00.028 --> 07:01.626
You're an artist.

07:01.627 --> 07:04.626
I mean, how long did it take
to do the Sistine Chapel?

07:04.627 --> 07:06.028
<font color="#00FFFF"> Dunno, wasn't one of mine.</font>

07:07.429 --> 07:09.626
It was Michelangelo,
and it took him four years.

07:09.627 --> 07:11.161
Do you know why?

07:11.162 --> 07:13.626
Cos he didn't have my wife
breathing down his neck.

07:13.627 --> 07:15.760
<font color="#00FFFF"> You know what I'm saying?</font>
Bending your ear, is she?</font>

07:15.761 --> 07:17.760
Oh, Dave, mate,
she's never off my back.

07:17.761 --> 07:21.161
<font color="#00FFFF"> Oh, I feel your pain, mate.</font>
Oh, yeah, your wife give you grief?

07:21.162 --> 07:22.626
<font color="#00FFFF"> Oh, you could say that.</font>

07:22.627 --> 07:24.162
<font color="#00FFFF"> She's dead.</font>

07:25.627 --> 07:27.626
Right. Sorry about that.

07:27.627 --> 07:28.627
<font color="#00FFFF"> Not really!</font>

07:30.627 --> 07:33.626
<font color="#00FFFF"> Got you there. </font>Ha-ha!
Bants, I love it.

07:33.627 --> 07:35.626
<font color="#00FFFF"> So how come I haven't met
your good lady yet?</font>

07:35.627 --> 07:38.626
Well, she likes to keep away
when the work's being done.

07:38.627 --> 07:41.626
She gets a bit petty about
not being able to cook or wash

07:41.627 --> 07:43.561
or having to breathe in asbestos.

07:43.562 --> 07:45.626
<font color="#00FFFF"> Ha! Women! </font>Yeah.</font>

07:45.627 --> 07:48.626
<font color="#00FFFF"> So I suppose this is a bit of a nice
holiday for you without her, eh?</font>

07:48.627 --> 07:51.626
<font color="#00FFFF"> Ha, yeah. </font>Yeah, you probably want me
to take as long as possible.</font>

07:51.627 --> 07:54.027
Oh, no, I really don't.

07:54.028 --> 07:56.626
No, she'll kill me if he's not ready
by the deadline,

07:56.627 --> 07:58.626
you know, this Friday.

07:58.627 --> 08:03.028
