08:11.162 --> 08:14.626
<font color="#00FFFF"> Oh, cheers, mate, that's brilliant.</font>
I wouldn't say that to just anyone,</font>

08:14.627 --> 08:16.894
<font color="#00FFFF"> but, as it's you, I'm going to
