08:16.895 --> 08:19.294
<font color="#00FFFF"> and make sure we finish
at the agreed time.</font>

08:19.295 --> 08:21.626
That's really good of you, cheers.

08:21.627 --> 08:25.626
So, just to be absolutely clear,
I can phone my wife now

08:25.627 --> 08:27.626
