going to be done by Friday?

08:27.627 --> 08:29.626
<font color="#00FFFF"> Absolutely. </font>Great!

08:29.627 --> 08:31.626
<font color="#00FFFF"> But if we need a plan B...</font>

08:31.627 --> 08:32.626
What?

08:32.628 --> 08:35.626
<font color="#00FFFF"> I'm just saying IF we need a plan B,
