08:35.626 --> 08:37.626
<font color="#00FFFF"> what we can do to get
your missus off your back, right,</font>

08:37.626 --> 08:40.626
<font color="#00FFFF"> is tell her we need a seven gauge
retractable pinion bracket.</font>

08:40.626 --> 08:43.626
