retractable pinion bracket?

08:43.626 --> 08:45.627
<font color="#00FFFF"> Bloody hope not!
There's no such thing.</font>

08:46.761 --> 08:49.626
<font color="#00FFFF"> What am I like?!</font>
I'm assuming that's rhetorical.

08:49.627 --> 08:51.626
But plan B won't be needed, right,

08:51.627 --> 08:53.760
because it'll definitely be done
by this Friday?

08:53.761 --> 08:57.561
<font color="#00FFFF"> No question,
absolutely 110% guaranteed.</font>

08:57.562 --> 08:58.626
OK.

08:58.627 --> 08:59.627
<font color="#00FFFF"> But if it isn't...</font>

09:00.627 --> 09:04.161
If it isn't? <font color="#00FFFF"> ..which it will be,
absolutely for certain... </font>Right.

09:04.162 --> 09:07.626
<font color="#00FFFF"> ..but if it isn't, then Monday
at the absolute latest.</font>

09:07.627 --> 09:09.429
<font color="#00FFFF"> Certainly no later than Tuesday.</font>

09:10.627 --> 09:12.627
<font color="#00FFFF"> Tuesday? </font>All being well.</font>

09:13.627 --> 09:14.627
<font color="#00FFFF"> Right, there it is.</font>

09:14.628 --> 09:15.895
<font color="#00FFFF"> Yep.</font>

09:19.627 --> 09:21.627
<font color="#00FFFF"> Oh, do us a favour, mate.</font>

09:36.627 --> 09:38.428
Oh. Hi, Anna.

09:38.429 --> 09:39.626
<font color="#FFFF00"> Hello, Lee. How are you?</font>

09:39.627 --> 09:42.027
<font color="#FFFF00"> Just seeing how things are going.</font>

09:42.028 --> 09:45.626
I think one of your earrings
