09:55.295 --> 09:57.627
<font color="#FFFF00"> I see. Toby said things
weren't quite going to plan.</font>

09:57.628 --> 09:59.626
<font color="#FFFF00"> Everything's under control. </font>Good.</font>

09:59.627 --> 10:02.028
<font color="#FFFF00"> Well, you won't mind me taking
a quick look, then.</font>

10:04.162 --> 10:07.428
<font color="#FFFF00"> Dear God, it's like the trenches
of World War I.</font>

10:07.429 --> 10:09.626
<font color="#FFFF00"> But with no poetry.</font>

10:09.627 --> 10:12.626
<font color="#FFFF00"> And even less chance of it
being finished by Christmas.</font>

10:12.627 --> 10:14.627
<font color="#FFFF00"> How did the work get so far behind?</font>

10:14.628 --> 10:17.626
Well, he's just waiting on
an essential part,

10:17.627 --> 10:19.627
a seven gauge
retractable pinion bracket.

10:21.162 --> 10:22.626
<font color="#FFFF00"> There's no such thing.</font>

10:22.627 --> 10:24.294
I know!

10:24.295 --> 10:25.626
<font color="#FFFF00"> Where is this builder, anyway?</font>

10:25.627 --> 10:28.027
<font color="#FFFF00"> He's at lunch. </font>It's 4pm!</font>

10:28.028 --> 10:31.294
Yeah, but, to be fair,
he didn't start till midday.

10:31.295 --> 10:33.626
<font color="#FFFF00"> This is appalling, Lee.
Look at the state of this place!</font>

10:33.627 --> 10:35.626
<font color="#FFFF00"> He's walked dirty boots
all over the rug.</font>

10:35.627 --> 10:39.626
<font color="#FFFF00"> Well, we haven't got a doormat.</font>
Well, that's a matter of opinion.</font>

10:39.627 --> 10:41.626
Look, I know she's your friend

10:41.627 --> 10:44.627
and you've only got her interests
at heart, but don't tell Lucy.

10:45.627 --> 10:47.626
Please.

10:47.627 --> 10:48.627
<font color="#FFFF00"> On one condition -</font>

10:48.628 --> 10:51.760
<font color="#FFFF00"> the moment this man gets back,
you give him a firm dressing down.</font>

10:51.761 --> 10:53.894
<font color="#FFFF00"> Get a written, detailed schedule
of each job</font>

10:53.895 --> 10:56.626
<font color="#FFFF00"> and when he's going to do it,
